{"tid":519920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣華醫院遺失149支病人血液樣本　標籤貼病人姓名、身份證號碼等","createTime":"2018-01-05T01:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T01:02:59.000Z","uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa99848f27afb2299d111cc4b3870ed5218575e8","tid":519920,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"醫院管理局今日(4日)公布，廣華醫院遺失149支病人血液樣本，樣本貼有列出病人姓名、身份證號碼、年齡和性別的標籤，至今仍未能尋獲，預料誤放於其他醫院，相信病人資料外洩風險較低。局方又指，延後進行血液測試不會對影響病人的治療。<br />\n<br />\n院方就是次事件致歉，並會成立小組檢視現有程序，分析根本原因和作出適當跟進改善措施。<br />\n個人資料私隱專員公署表示，已收到醫院管理局就有關事件的口頭知會，會跟進了解有關詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/146768/%E5%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1149%E6%94%AF%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4%E8%B2%BC%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E5%A7%93%E5%90%8D-%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E7%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F146768%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1149%25E6%2594%25AF%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B6%25B2%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%25B1%25A4%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A7%2593%25E5%2590%258D-%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%25AD%2589&d=wxO4TvblOyXzBSP4btRs826tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=42ddd8d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/146768/%E5%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1149%E6%94%AF%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4%E8%B2%BC%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E5%A7%93%E5%90%8D-%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E7%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"7c326ace895156ac44e6a26d96d136490aa258e4","tid":519920,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"屌那星，即係又要再抽過"}]}